ocl:
context Reservation
inv: self.dateTo <> null and self.createdAt <> null

context Branch
inv: self.name.size() >= 10 implies self.name.substring(1, 10) = 'value'

context Reservation
inv: (self.dateTo <> null and self.dateFrom <> null) or (self.dateTo = null and self.dateFrom = null)

context Branch
inv: self.capacity >= 79 and self.capacity <= 99

context Branch
inv: if self.isOpen then self.capacity <> null else self.name <> null endif

context Vehicle
inv: self.reservations->size() >= 2 and self.reservations->size() <= 2

context Customer
inv: self.age >= 18 and self.age <= 20

context Payment
inv: self.timestamp.size() >= 5 implies self.timestamp.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context Vehicle
inv: self.reservations->notEmpty() implies self.reservations->first().isConfirmed <> null

context Rental
inv: self.mileageEnd >= 24 and self.mileageEnd <= 63

context Company
inv: self.name <> '' and self.name.size() > 0

context Rental
inv: self.endDate <> null implies self.startDate <> null

context Customer
inv: self.reservations->notEmpty() implies self.reservations->last().dateTo <> null

context Company
inv: self.branches->notEmpty() implies self.branches->sortedBy(x | x.capacity)->first().capacity <= self.branches->sortedBy(x | x.capacity)->last().capacity

context Reservation
inv: not(self.dateTo <> null and self.createdAt <> null)

context Rental
inv: not((self.mileageStart <> null) = (self.mileageEnd <> null))

context Vehicle
inv: (self.mileage >= 3 and self.mileage <= 80) and (self.mileage < 3)

context Rental
inv: not((self.mileageStart <> null and self.mileageEnd <> null) or (self.mileageStart = null and self.mileageEnd = null))
